		"description": "This collection demonstrates **file upload API testing**.\n\nThe APIs are tested using **`file-upload-RestAPI.jar`**.\n\n<u><b>Setup Instructions:</b></u>\n\n- Run the application using the command below in **administrator mode** from the directory where the JAR file is located:  \n    `java -jar file-upload-RestAPI.jar`\n    \n- Open a browser and verify the application is running:  \n    [<code>http://localhost:8080/</code>](http://localhost:8080/)\n    \n\n### Upload APIs:\n\n- POST [http://localhost:8080/uploadFile](http://localhost:8080/uploadFile)\n    \n- POST [http://localhost:8080/uploadMultipleFiles](http://localhost:8080/uploadMultipleFiles)\n    \n\n### How to Attach Files in Postman:\n\n- Go to **Body â†’ form-data**\n    \n- **Single File Upload**\n    \n    - Key: `file`\n        \n    - Type: `File`\n        \n- **Multiple File Upload**\n    \n    - Key: `files`\n        \n    - Type: `File`",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "21963655"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Single File Upload",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"let jsonData = pm.response.json();\r",
							"pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function(){\r",
							"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);\r",
							"});\r",
							"\r",
							"pm.test(\"Response has all required fields\", function(){\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property(\"fileName\");\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property(\"fileDownloadUri\");\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property(\"fileType\");\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property(\"size\");  \r",
							"});\r",
							"\r",
							"pm.test(\"File name validation\", function(){\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.fileName).to.eql(\"Test2.txt\");\r",
							"});\r",
							"\r",
							"pm.test(\"Response time < 500ms\", function(){\r",
							"    pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(500);\r",
							"});\r",
							"\r",
							"pm.test(\"File type is text/plain\", function () {\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.fileType).to.equal(\"text/plain\");\r",
							"});\r",
							"\r",
							"pm.test(\"file download url validation\", function(){\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.fileDownloadUri).to.include(\"/downloadFile/\");\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.fileDownloadUri).to.match(/^http:\\/\\/localhost:8080/);  \r",
							"});\r",
							"\r",
							"pm.test(\"File size validation\", function () {\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.size).to.be.a(\"number\");\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.size).to.be.at.least(0);\r",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.size).to.be.above(0);\r",
							"});"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript",
						"packages": {},
						"requests": {}
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [],
				"body": {
					"mode": "formdata",
					"formdata": [
						{
							"key": "file",
							"type": "file",
							"src": "/C:/Users/Prem/OneDrive/Desktop/Personal Details/API-Learning/file-upload-jar/Test2.txt"
						}
					]
				},
				"url": {
